    "description": "<p>ISPL Pte. Ltd. is the leading Sound &amp; Visual Communications Technology Solutions Provider since 2002. We create innovative, scalable, professional and reliable state-of-the-art solutions which suit our clients' facilities and daily operation.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We provide system integration solutions for Healthcare Communication, Network Communication, Wireless &amp; Voice Communications, and Other Systems such as Audio/Visual and Other Extra Low Voltage (\"ELV\") Systems.</p>\n<p>Our key success factor is the ability to deliver technology solutions with unparalleled simplicity.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We maintain constant interaction with our clients from concept to completion and ensure the solution meets their requirement and exceeds their expectation.</p>",
